---
title: "_getAssetOutAmount (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_clamp: elapsedTime = min(elapsedTime, auctionDuration)
    q_clamp --> q_multiplier: compute priceMultiplier
    q_multiplier --> q_get_assetout_price: priceMultiplier = start - (start - end) * elapsed / duration
    q_get_assetout_price --> q_usd_value: assetOutUsdPrice = getAssetPrice(s_assetOut, withValidation)
    q_usd_value --> q_convert: auctionUsdValue = amountIn * assetInPrice / 10^decimals * priceMultiplier (roundUp)
    q_convert --> [*]: return auctionUsdValue * 10^assetOutDecimals / assetOutUsdPrice (roundUp)

    note right of q_multiplier
        INV-015: Linear decay from startingPriceMultiplier to endingPriceMultiplier over auctionDuration
    end note

    note right of q_usd_value
        INV-016: mulDivUp and mulWadUp used - rounds UP in favor of protocol (bidder pays more)
    end note

    note right of q_convert
        INV-017: Final conversion also rounds UP - bidder always pays ceiling amount
    end note
